1
00:00:09,114 --> 00:00:13,160
♪I defy heaven, fate,
and so-called immortality♪

2
00:00:13,160 --> 00:00:17,800
♪At last you say
we've been apart too long♪

3
00:00:17,800 --> 00:00:22,840
♪Unwilling, unyielding, I won't let go♪

4
00:00:22,840 --> 00:00:28,000
♪With you, even a dried sea
learns to embrace a stream♪

5
00:00:28,000 --> 00:00:32,415
♪If heaven divides us, I'll reunite us,
with love as our vessel♪

6
00:00:32,415 --> 00:00:37,167
♪If it forbids it, I'll shatter
the absurd Heavenly Dao♪

7
00:00:37,167 --> 00:00:42,400
♪Even if countless stars
turn into my foes♪

8
00:00:42,400 --> 00:00:47,853
♪To grow old with you, we burn
through the end of the long night♪

9
00:00:50,820 --> 00:00:55,760
=Rise Again=

10
00:00:56,144 --> 00:00:58,878
=Episode 10=

11
00:01:23,920 --> 00:01:24,719
Who are you?

12
00:01:31,840 --> 00:01:32,760
Why is it you?

13
00:01:33,079 --> 00:01:33,840
Where's Ningxue?

14
00:01:35,400 --> 00:01:37,400
Why can't it be me?

15
00:01:46,000 --> 00:01:46,799
Where is Ningxue?

16
00:01:47,519 --> 00:01:48,319
Ningxue?

17
00:01:49,439 --> 00:01:50,840
Is she really that important to you?

18
00:01:52,439 --> 00:01:54,719
Am I not good enough for you?

19
00:01:55,239 --> 00:01:56,319
Or...

20
00:01:57,359 --> 00:01:58,760
are you just not up to it?

21
00:02:10,439 --> 00:02:11,280
Like what you see?

22
00:02:12,439 --> 00:02:13,840
Tonight, it's just the two of us.

23
00:02:14,080 --> 00:02:15,400
If you stay,

24
00:02:16,199 --> 00:02:17,319
I'll let you take it all in.

25
00:02:17,919 --> 00:02:19,439
What exactly are you trying to do?

26
00:02:22,680 --> 00:02:24,199
Don't play dumb.

27
00:02:25,599 --> 00:02:27,120
Of course I want to do

28
00:02:27,120 --> 00:02:28,840
what all men want to do.

29
00:02:30,080 --> 00:02:31,280
Cut it out, will you?

30
00:02:32,080 --> 00:02:33,479
Ningxue is your best friend.

31
00:02:34,080 --> 00:02:35,400
Is this really how you treat her?

32
00:02:37,479 --> 00:02:38,439
I already told you,

33
00:02:38,680 --> 00:02:40,479
tonight it's just the two of us.

34
00:02:40,599 --> 00:02:42,280
You don't have to worry about
Ningxue finding out.

35
00:02:44,240 --> 00:02:45,080
Just the two of us.

36
00:02:45,800 --> 00:02:46,599
You sure about that?

37
00:02:51,199 --> 00:02:52,080
Of course.

38
00:02:57,199 --> 00:02:58,159
I've gone this far.

39
00:02:58,159 --> 00:02:59,080
You're still not biting?

40
00:02:59,080 --> 00:03:00,319
What, are you dense or something?

41
00:03:10,240 --> 00:03:11,400
Why aren't you fighting back?

42
00:03:13,639 --> 00:03:14,919
Do you look down on me or something?

43
00:03:19,879 --> 00:03:21,280
If I hurt you,

44
00:03:21,280 --> 00:03:22,599
how will I explain it to Ningxue?

45
00:03:22,840 --> 00:03:23,800
You think you're that tough?

46
00:03:23,800 --> 00:03:25,120
Don't go easy on me.

47
00:03:28,039 --> 00:03:29,120
You pervert.

48
00:03:34,719 --> 00:03:36,080
If you've got guts, let me get up.

49
00:03:36,199 --> 00:03:38,039
Let me change,
then we'll go another round.

50
00:03:39,479 --> 00:03:40,680
Give it 15 minutes,

51
00:03:40,840 --> 00:03:42,280
and the power will fade on its own.

52
00:03:42,520 --> 00:03:43,000
Perfect.

53
00:03:43,759 --> 00:03:44,759
Use this time

54
00:03:45,240 --> 00:03:46,719
to train your lower body stability.

55
00:03:48,840 --> 00:03:49,639
Su Wubing.

56
00:03:50,919 --> 00:03:51,840
Turn around.

57
00:03:52,800 --> 00:03:53,599
Now what?

58
00:03:54,240 --> 00:03:55,280
Have you thought about this...

59
00:03:55,719 --> 00:03:57,919
If one day something happens to Ningxue,

60
00:03:57,919 --> 00:03:59,879
and saving her means sacrificing you,

61
00:04:00,240 --> 00:04:01,199
what would you do?

62
00:04:05,039 --> 00:04:06,439
If that day really comes,

63
00:04:07,319 --> 00:04:08,520
I wouldn't wait for her to ask.

64
00:04:09,319 --> 00:04:10,599
I'd go on my own

65
00:04:11,479 --> 00:04:13,199
and sacrifice my life for hers.

66
00:04:14,240 --> 00:04:15,520
I wouldn't hesitate.

67
00:04:16,199 --> 00:04:17,000
After all...

68
00:04:18,879 --> 00:04:19,800
it's not the first time.

69
00:04:26,800 --> 00:04:27,600
Yingying.

70
00:04:33,040 --> 00:04:34,439
I told you,

71
00:04:34,600 --> 00:04:35,600
even testing him like that,

72
00:04:35,800 --> 00:04:37,199
he's not that kind of guy.

73
00:04:37,439 --> 00:04:38,480
He did that on purpose.

74
00:04:38,480 --> 00:04:40,600
He saw right through us.

75
00:04:41,720 --> 00:04:43,399
Alright, alright, don't be mad.

76
00:04:43,399 --> 00:04:45,680
I'll try to get you out of this first.

77
00:04:51,279 --> 00:04:52,079
Unbelievable.

78
00:05:05,560 --> 00:05:08,160
Su Wubing, hurry, save me!

79
00:05:09,240 --> 00:05:10,040
What a coincidence.

80
00:05:20,639 --> 00:05:23,199
Su Wubing, you finally came.

81
00:05:45,399 --> 00:05:48,079
I thought you wouldn't show up.

82
00:05:48,920 --> 00:05:50,480
That jerk Gu Yuanbing

83
00:05:50,720 --> 00:05:52,040
found out we know each other,

84
00:05:52,439 --> 00:05:54,079
so he tried to give me
away to someone else.

85
00:05:55,279 --> 00:05:56,199
I refused,

86
00:05:57,040 --> 00:05:58,600
so he tied me up here.

87
00:05:59,680 --> 00:06:00,800
Put your clothes on.

88
00:06:01,040 --> 00:06:02,040
I'll get you out of here.

89
00:06:06,639 --> 00:06:08,759
Gu Yuanbing made me take something.

90
00:06:09,319 --> 00:06:11,519
I feel weak all over right now.

91
00:06:12,759 --> 00:06:13,959
I'm so hot...

92
00:06:16,879 --> 00:06:17,839
Feel that?

93
00:06:18,079 --> 00:06:20,560
My heart's beating so fast.

94
00:06:21,279 --> 00:06:22,079
Let go.

95
00:06:27,399 --> 00:06:28,720
Come on, just listen.

96
00:06:30,480 --> 00:06:31,279
Thump.

97
00:06:32,319 --> 00:06:33,120
Thump, thump.

98
00:06:34,279 --> 00:06:36,000
My heart's racing like this

99
00:06:36,720 --> 00:06:38,079
all because of you.

100
00:06:39,480 --> 00:06:40,639
Can you hear it?

101
00:06:42,680 --> 00:06:44,040
Looks like Mr. Gu was right.

102
00:06:44,240 --> 00:06:46,079
No matter how tough Su Wubing is,

103
00:06:46,079 --> 00:06:48,439
he can't resist a woman
throwing herself at him.

104
00:06:49,040 --> 00:06:50,319
So you called me here

105
00:06:51,040 --> 00:06:52,480
just to tell me all this?

106
00:07:09,120 --> 00:07:10,600
I remember when I first came in,

107
00:07:11,519 --> 00:07:13,319
you were tied up all over.

108
00:07:14,800 --> 00:07:16,199
So how did you call me?

109
00:07:19,439 --> 00:07:21,399
I don't remember anything...

110
00:07:22,360 --> 00:07:23,399
I'm so hot...

111
00:07:33,360 --> 00:07:34,160
All of this

112
00:07:35,600 --> 00:07:37,199
was set up by Gu Yuanbing, wasn't it?

113
00:07:41,079 --> 00:07:42,279
Su Wubing, you!

114
00:07:45,079 --> 00:07:45,879
Su Wubing!

115
00:07:51,680 --> 00:07:52,600
Su Wubing!

116
00:07:52,600 --> 00:07:54,680
Next time, I won't let him off.

117
00:07:55,399 --> 00:07:56,600
Now you can rest easy, right?

118
00:07:56,600 --> 00:07:58,360
He isn't the kind of person
you said he was.

119
00:07:58,360 --> 00:07:59,480
This doesn't count.

120
00:07:59,480 --> 00:08:00,920
He definitely knew you were here.

121
00:08:30,721 --> 00:08:34,824
♪I defy heaven, fate,
and so-called immortality♪

122
00:08:34,824 --> 00:08:39,544
♪At last you say
we've been apart too long♪

123
00:08:39,544 --> 00:08:44,424
♪Unwilling, unyielding, I won't let go♪

124
00:08:44,424 --> 00:08:49,544
♪With you, even a dried sea
learns to embrace a stream♪

125
00:08:49,544 --> 00:08:53,944
♪If heaven divides us, I'll reunite us,
with love as our vessel♪

126
00:08:53,944 --> 00:08:58,624
♪If it forbids it, I'll shatter
the absurd Heavenly Dao♪

127
00:08:58,624 --> 00:09:04,024
♪Even if countless stars
turn into my foes♪

128
00:09:04,024 --> 00:09:10,418
♪To grow old with you, we burn
through the end of the long night♪
